spec_data.Name: python2-flufl-lock
spec_data.Description:
The flufl.lock library provides an NFS-safe file-based locking algorithm
influenced by the GNU/Linux "open(2)" man page, under the description of
the "O_EXCL" option.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 23 Feb 2017 10:42:38 AM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: NFS-safe file locking with timeouts for POSIX systems
